## TR | Kurallar
- //@version=6 ile başla
- LESSONS_LEARNED.md oku (kod yazmadan önce)
- LLM_MANIFEST.md ile dosya bul
- ta.* kullan, manuel yazma
- Hata çözümünü LESSONS_LEARNED.md'ye ekle

## EN | Rules
- Start with //@version=6
- Read LESSONS_LEARNED.md before writing code
- Use LLM_MANIFEST.md to find the right reference file
- Use ta.* — never reimplement
- Append error fixes to LESSONS_LEARNED.md

